<item>
            <title>[FLINK-6213] When number of failed containers exceeds maximum failed containers and application is stopped, the AM container will be released 10 minutes later </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-6213</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When number of failed containers exceeds maximum failed containers and application is stopped, the AM container will be released 10 minutes later. I checked yarn log and found out after invoking &lt;tt&gt;unregisterApplicationMaster&lt;/tt&gt;, the AM container is not released. After 10 minutes, the release is triggered by RM ping check timeout.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="13059966">FLINK-6213</key>
